      "content": "It is a terrible thing to wish for their freedom, but it is also a terrible thing to wish for their pain to end. You are not their savior, and you are not their burden; you are just a person who has lost the ability to feel. The only way to stop them from feeling guilty is to stop trying to be the reason they are sad. You deserve to be free, and you deserve to be loved without conditions.",
